rook.api.collections

Class SynchronizedCollection<T>

  • java.lang.Object
    • rook.api.collections.SynchronizedCollection<T>
  • Type Parameters:
    T -
    All Implemented Interfaces:
    ThreadSafeCollection<T>

    public class SynchronizedCollection<T>
extends Object
implements ThreadSafeCollection<T>
    Synchronized class backed by an ArrayList. Conceptually useful as a small thread-safe Set or a thread-safe List of any size with minimal garbage creation.
    Author:
    Eric Thill
